'''Pantsing''' is the action of yanking down someone's pants or both their pants and underwear. It can be inferred from the game that it's solely the act of yanking down one's pants solely. You will see this feedback pop up every so often when you choose to mess with a person.

You can randomly stumble across this action when you mess with someone while in ''school.'' Additionally, while in prison, you can elect to mess with them via going to the prison yard, selecting a name and click “mess with them.” If in school, go to class, pick a name, click “mess”. 

